cs.CR, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.CC, cs.IT 

This paper deals with cryptographic hash functions and neural networks, which are topics related to computer security (cs.CR), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and machine learning (cs.LG). The use of fuzzy bits and the inversion of hash functions also involve concepts from coding theory (cs.CC) and information theory (cs.IT).
